      <Value><![CDATA[<p>The Student Funding Adviser provides one-to-one information, advice and guidance on the funding available to you when you are studying with us, including:</p>
<ul>
<li>Loans, bursaries and tuition fees</li>
<li>Benefits and studying</li>
<li>Childcare Fund</li>
<li>Discretionary Fund (formerly the Hardship Fund)</li>
<li>Nursing Discretionary Fund</li>
<li>International Hardship Fund</li>
<li>Post-graduate funding</li>
<li>Part-time funding</li>
</ul>
<p class="x_MsoNormal">If you have any concerns about your financial situation then please contact the Funding Adviser at <a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="mailto:%20studentfunding@qmu.ac.uk" target="_blank" data-auth="NotApplicable" data-linkindex="1">studentfunding@qmu.ac.uk</a></p>
<p class="x_MsoNormal"><a rel="noopener" href="https://studentcentral.qmu.ac.uk/s/student-funding/appointments/" target="_blank" title="Student Funding Appointment"><span class="lead">Book an appointment with the Student Funding Adviser.</span></a></p>
<p class="x_MsoNormal"> </p>]]></Value>
