    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p><span class="lead lead-big"><strong>Applications for 2023/2024 are now open</strong></span></p>
<p>Applications to the Discretionary Fund (formerly the Hardship fund), the Childcare fund and the Nursing Discretionary fund for 2023/2024 are open.</p>
<p><strong>Please note that the International Hardship fund (for students from outside the UK) for 2023/2024 is now closed and cannot accept any further applications.</strong></p>]]></Value>
